    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, F, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Make a single attack with your held projectile weapon. The attack gains a Kawarimi Defense of 1 per 4 levels (up to 5). A Samurai with at least 2 class levels may substitute this technique for a normal attack when they make a Full Attack (using the same attack bonus as the substituted attack), but only if they chose the Kyujutsu path. If you substitute the technique this way, it cannot be empowered and the Perform Requirements are automatically met.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 3 Chakra to have the attack deal 1d6 bonus damage, plus 1d6 per 4 levels(up to 5d6).</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
